{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"128209-el-ekhersito-dey-las-burbookhas","title":"El ejército de las burbujas","description":"A Bunty no le gusta el jabón, por eso siempre se niega a limpiarse. Pero una noche tiene un sueño. ¿Qué pasa después entonces?","language":"Spanish","langCode":"es","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Aboli Chowdhary"],"illustrators":["Sorit Gupto"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/128209-el-ekhersito-dey-las-burbookhas"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/720260/size3/bfaca307e321a40d4fce0bf9bade9047.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/720260/size6/bfaca307e321a40d4fce0bf9bade9047.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2386/size6/9907217108246f4eb01c1ac7f252464b.jpg","text":"A Bunty le encanta jugar con las mariposas...","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2387/size6/3cfef50c731271c06bc7df15adfad696.jpg","text":"...y con los pájaros.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2388/size6/0b2cc2ad4ba1e7c14ab8f85d1cc92a02.jpg","text":"Le encanta jugar con los botes de papel.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2389/size6/1fea81780050ff2039ff47dedfb38216.jpg","text":"También le gusta hacer castillos de arena.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2390/size6/b4b058041a0f8816ef576bb510e2a358.jpg","text":"Cuando Bunty vuelve a casa,\nSu madre le pide que limpie.\n \nPero ella se niega a limpiarse.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2391/size6/f13b791f09d8c65688476d9d6782ede2.jpg","text":"\"¡Odio los jabones!\" ella grita.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2392/size6/45170485855b821bd3a27a6917664b6f.jpg","text":"Una noche, tiene un sueño.\nLos gérmenes están rodeando su castillo, y la están atacando...","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2393/size6/05cc5eb1bd0a44d4e01e16ad4432d8fd.jpg","text":"Los gérmenes corren tras Bunty.\nElla corre por su vida y grita, \"¡Ayuda!... ¡Ayuda!\"","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2394/size6/c3075a8fd3d40bc48a3983ac434329a7.jpg","text":"De repente, el Rey Jabón Burbujo aparece.\n\"Bunty, no tengas miedo\", dice. ¡Ataque los gérmenes! \nle ordena el Rey Jabón a su ejército de burbujas.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2395/size6/9e0c56e80240c4c4448a07ac8d9e80c0.jpg","text":"El ejército de burbujas ahuyenta a los gérmenes.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2396/size6/342fa90cc8f644b89f8b05984faab025.jpg","text":"En estos días, a Bunty le gusta usar jabón,\n \nY se cepilla y se limpia a fondo.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":128}}